Could you please help me?

265
00:18:29,409 --> 00:18:30,909
yes.

266
00:18:31,911 --> 00:18:33,911
(sound of opening bag)

267
00:18:35,415 --> 00:18:36,916
Huh?

268
00:18:36,916 --> 00:18:39,419
To... meat buns?

269
00:18:39,419 --> 00:18:40,919
It's meat bun.

270
00:18:42,422 --> 00:18:45,425
It was written in the book that it was a standard after-school date➡

271
00:18:45,425 --> 00:18:47,925
It was prepared by the hotel.

272
00:18:50,430 --> 00:18:54,867
Fufufu… haha!

273
00:18:54,867 --> 00:18:57,870
In this sparkling space➡

274
00:18:57,870 --> 00:19:00,373
Meat bun!

275
00:19:00,373 --> 00:19:02,375
Didn't like it?

276
00:19:02,375 --> 00:19:03,876
Ah, no.

277
00:19:03,876 --> 00:19:06,876
There's something about Kurosaki-san.

278
00:19:08,881 --> 00:19:12,381
I like this about Kurosaki-san.

279
00:19:15,388 --> 00:19:18,888
like…?

280
00:19:21,394 --> 00:19:24,397
Mr. Koharu.

281
00:19:24,397 --> 00:19:26,899
I like you too.

282
00:19:26,899 --> 00:19:29,402
From my heart.

283
00:19:29,402 --> 00:19:45,418
♬～

284
00:19:45,418 --> 00:19:49,422
Smartphone) (vibrating sound)

285
00:19:49,422 --> 00:19:52,425
Mr. Kurosaki, you should answer the phone...Smartphone) (vibrating sound)

286
00:19:52,425 --> 00:19:56,863
Smartphone) (vibrating sound)

287
00:19:56,863 --> 00:19:58,865
Ha, sorry.

288
00:19:58,865 --> 00:20:01,868
Kiriya-san, please excuse me for a moment.

289
00:20:01,868 --> 00:20:03,368
yes.

290
00:20:05,371 --> 00:20:07,371
Thank you for your hard work.

291
00:20:08,374 --> 00:20:12,378
《Are you so excited about going on a date after becoming a lover? 》

292
00:20:12,378 --> 00:20:14,878
《I don't have a heart anymore~》

293
00:20:16,883 --> 00:20:18,885
Mr. Koharu.

294
00:20:18,885 --> 00:20:21,888
I would like you to check the manuscript as soon as possible➡

295
00:20:21,888 --> 00:20:24,390
I have to go home.

296
00:20:24,390 --> 00:20:25,892
sorry.

297
00:20:25,892 --> 00:20:30,392
Yes, it's work, and I've had a lot of fun.

298
00:20:31,898 --> 00:20:34,901
Oh, and actually➡

299
00:20:34,901 --> 00:20:38,404
There are autograph sessions planned around the country starting next week➡

300
00:20:38,404 --> 00:20:41,407
I think I won't be able to see you for a while.

301
00:20:41,407 --> 00:20:43,409
Understood.

302
00:20:43,409 --> 00:20:46,409
I'll be waiting for you to come back, so please do your best.

303
00:20:48,414 --> 00:20:49,916
I don't like it.

304
00:20:49,916 --> 00:20:51,416
picture…?

305
00:20:54,854 --> 00:20:57,857
I want to do this with Koharu-san.

306
00:20:57,857 --> 00:21:00,357
Da... no.

307
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:03,362
If so.

308
00:21:03,362 --> 00:21:05,362
(sound of opening bag)

309
00:21:06,866 --> 00:21:08,866
Even just here.

310
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:13,372
Why is this happening now?

311
00:21:13,372 --> 00:21:15,374
Please. No.

312
00:21:15,374 --> 00:21:17,376
please! No!

313
00:21:17,376 --> 00:21:20,376
Thank you! No!

314
00:21:21,881 --> 00:21:23,881
I got it….

315
00:21:25,384 --> 00:21:27,887
Good luck with your work.

316
00:21:27,887 --> 00:21:29,889
I really don't like it. It's no good.

317
00:21:29,889 --> 00:21:31,389
please.

318
00:21:43,903 --> 00:21:46,405
Thank you for waiting, Mom.

319
00:21:46,405 --> 00:21:49,405
You finished shopping quickly.

320
00:21:52,411 --> 00:21:56,811
(Ai) There was an article about that girl again.

321
00:21:58,351 --> 00:21:59,852
Ah, now that I think about it...

322
00:21:59,852 --> 00:22:02,352
how are you these days?

323
00:22:03,856 --> 00:22:08,861
I'm a college student, so it's the same as usual.

324
00:22:08,861 --> 00:22:13,366
Don't worry, I'm doing well. What are you saying stupidly?

325
00:22:13,366 --> 00:22:16,869
If you say such carefree things, you won't win!?

326
00:22:16,869 --> 00:22:19,372
Even though that kid is getting such results➡

327
00:22:19,372 --> 00:22:22,375
Aren't you frustrated?

328
00:22:22,375 --> 00:22:28,381
♬～

329
00:22:28,381 --> 00:22:32,381
(Sound of holding hands) Hey Yuio?

330
00:22:34,387 --> 00:22:38,891
Don't let your mother down.

331
00:22:38,891 --> 00:22:43,396
♬～

332
00:22:43,396 --> 00:22:45,898
Phew...｡

333
00:22:45,898 --> 00:22:47,898
I understand.

334
00:22:51,404 --> 00:22:53,839
It's okay if you're serious.

335
00:22:53,839 --> 00:23:01,839
♬～
